(243, 1, '2014-05-27 13:46:47', '2014-05-27 13:46:47', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Daily Home Ltd</b> was formed to cater the boom in Real Estate Development in Bangladesh with a mission to ensure a better lifestyle with a smart benefit scheme to our clients and Land Owners. Innovation and improvisation is two of our key strength which are driving us to be committed to ensure unique and hassle free Customer Service and be the ultimate in the property solution in Bangladesh.d</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The motto of <b>Daily Home Ltd</b> is not only to deliver apartment ahead of schedule but also to maintain the highest-grade construction quality that has gained trust and respect in customers. We feel our customers deserve nothing less than the best, and we are committed to deliver it.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Like the meaning of our company name ‘Daily Home’, we want all our customers to feel daily home in touch with us. All their suggestions and advice\'s are considered and worked on with the greatest of care and dedication. We hope that we shall continue to be blessed with such support as we have experienced over our short tenure.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Beside these <b>Daily Home Ltd</b> comprises of one best professional team to deliver beyond their capacity. The team dedicated to the company, comes with vast real estate background to ensure highest-grade of construction quality.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We hope you will embrace our venture with open arms and also enrich us with your valuable advice\'s and suggestions. We expect your support in every step we take.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>Mr. Salahuddin Mahmud Jahid</strong></em>\r\n<em><strong> Managing Director</strong></em>\r\n<em><strong> Daily Home Limited.</strong></em></p>', 'Message from The Managing Director', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'message', '', '', '2019-09-26 12:12:33', '2019-09-26 12:12:33', '', 0, 'http://localhost/dailyhome//?page_id=243', 0, 'page', '', 0),
