(512, 1, '2016-05-11 12:09:09', '2016-05-11 12:09:09', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Daily Home Ltd</b> is one of the growing Real Estate Companies in Bangladesh. It starts journey through developing complexes apartment in prime locations on Dhaka city since 2015. It is also a member of Real Estate &amp; Housing Association of Bangladesh (REHAB) &amp; Registerd with RAJUK.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Within a short span of time <b><b>Daily Home Ltd</b> </b>has become a trusted name in the real estate Sector in Bangladesh From its very inception ,the company has won the confidence and goodwill of its clients into growing itself up to a renowned and dependable organization. <b>Daily Home Ltd</b> became as a specialist in building elegant and aesthetically pleasing structures that graces Dhaka a great city.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Daily Home Ltd</b> uses the highest quality of building materials and finishing products to ensure durability and customer satisfaction. The most important concentration of comfort Living have been in the prime, attractive location of Dhaka city,the emphasis being on sound construction and aesthetic design.In addition, Comfort Living is trying to provide accommodation suitable for small families while creating Scope for development of residential lands in the vicinity of the capital city . The success of such a large construction  company requires Specialized labours and highly qualified professional back up Comfort Living using a strong team of such highly skilled and experienced professionals to work under its competent management, has successfully prove its track record, Living  to  every body’s expectation.</p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-11 12:09:09', '2016-05-11 12:09:09', '', 12, 'http://localhost/dailyhome//?p=512', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(513, 1, '2016-05-11 12:12:48', '2016-05-11 12:12:48', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"http://localhost/dailyhome//wp-content/uploads/2014/05/sarower-chairman.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-270 alignleft\" alt=\"sarower-chairman\" src=\"http://localhost/dailyhome//wp-content/uploads/2014/05/sarower-chairman.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"142\" /></a><b>Daily Home Ltd</b> was formed to cater the boom in Real Estate Development in Bangladesh with a mission to ensure a better lifestyle with a smart benefit scheme to our clients and Land Owners. Innovation and improvisation is two of our key strength which are driving us to be committed to ensure unique and hassle free Customer Service and be the ultimate in the property solution in Bangladesh.d</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The motto of <b>Daily Home Ltd</b> is not only to deliver apartment ahead of schedule but also to maintain the highest-grade construction quality that has gained trust and respect in customers. We feel our customers deserve nothing less than the best, and we are committed to deliver it.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Like the meaning of our company name ‘Comfort’, we want all our customers to feel comfort in touch with us. All their suggestions and advice\'s are considered and worked on with the greatest of care and dedication. We hope that we shall continue to be blessed with such support as we have experienced over our short tenure.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Beside these <b>Daily Home Ltd</b> comprises of one best professional team to deliver beyond their capacity. The team dedicated to the company, comes with vast real estate background to ensure highest-grade of construction quality.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We hope you will embrace our venture with open arms and also enrich us with your valuable advice\'s and suggestions. We expect your support in every step we take.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>Mr. Sal</strong></em>\r\n<em><strong> Chairman</strong></em>\r\n<em><strong> Daily Home Limited.</strong></em></p>', 'Message from The Chairman', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '243-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-11 12:12:48', '2016-05-11 12:12:48', '', 243, 'http://localhost/dailyhome//?p=513', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
